---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="LDI — Yasuragi / Deep Garden" description="A quiet place behind the noise. Yasuragi Garden above, Deep Garden below." activePage="/deep-garden">

  <!-- Depth marker -->
  <aside class="depth-marker" aria-label="Garden depth position">
    <a href="#yasuragi" class="depth-link active" data-depth="yasuragi"><span class="depth-dot"></span>Yasuragi</a>
    <a href="#root-layer" class="depth-link" data-depth="root-layer"><span class="depth-dot"></span>Root Layer</a>
    <a href="#deep-garden" class="depth-link" data-depth="deep-garden"><span class="depth-dot"></span>Deep Garden</a>
  </aside>

  <!-- ── 01. Surface Garden ── -->
  <section id="surface-garden" class="garden-section surface-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <header class="section-head">
        <p class="eyebrow">ACC. ROOT-001</p>
        <h2>Visible Root System<br>Restorative Zone</h2>
        <p class="section-copy">
          Yasuragi Garden is the visible layer of the garden system — cultivated, tended, and accessible.
          This is where the attraction softens. Where noise drains off.
          Where ideas can rest long enough to become clear again.
        </p>
        <p class="section-note">Not every path needs to lead somewhere loud.</p>
      </header>

      <div class="artifact-grid">
        <article class="artifact-card">
          <span class="artifact-idx">01</span>
          <h3>Bonsai Registry</h3>
          <p>Atlas, Patient Zero, Lantern Keeper, and Quiet Signal remain under active care.</p>
          <small>Warden note: do not rush the small trees.</small>
        </article>
        <article class="artifact-card">
          <span class="artifact-idx">02</span>
          <h3>Lantern Path</h3>
          <p>Teal lanterns mark safe routes. Dim lanterns indicate slow zones. Flicker does not always mean danger.</p>
          <small>Current lantern status: all lit.</small>
        </article>
        <article class="artifact-card quote-card">
          <span class="artifact-idx">03</span>
          <h3>Warden's Bench</h3>
          <blockquote>"Urgency is often just unprocessed fear wearing a watch."</blockquote>
        </article>
        <article class="artifact-card">
          <span class="artifact-idx">04</span>
          <h3>Greenhouse Notes</h3>
          <p>Glass cleaned after storm activity. Rain chain repaired. Roots visible near west wall.</p>
          <small>Filed under: ordinary miracles.</small>
        </article>
        <article class="artifact-card">
          <span class="artifact-idx">05</span>
          <h3>Stone Basin</h3>
          <p>Touch water. Breathe. Begin again.</p>
          <small>Water recirculating normally.</small>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 02. Root Layer Descent (pinned scroll: surface → roots → deep) ── -->
  <section id="yasuragi" class="descent-stage" aria-label="Garden descent from surface to deep">
    <div class="descent-viewport">
      <div class="motion-layer surface-image" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="motion-layer cutaway-image" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="motion-layer deep-image" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="motion-layer leaves-layer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="motion-layer roots-layer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="motion-layer signal-layer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="motion-layer mist-layer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="motion-layer shaft-vignette-layer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="descent-copy" data-copy="surface">
        <p class="eyebrow">Warden Collection</p>
        <h2>Yasuragi<br>Garden</h2>
        <p>A quiet place behind the noise.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="descent-copy" data-copy="root">
        <p class="eyebrow">Root Layer</p>
        <h2>Below the visible garden<br>is the part that remembers.</h2>
        <p>Some ideas are not dead. They are just underground.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="descent-copy" data-copy="deep">
        <p class="eyebrow">ACC. ROOT-002</p>
        <h2>Deep<br>Garden</h2>
        <p>Memory compost / dormant idea storage.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 03. Root Map ── -->
  <section id="root-layer" class="garden-section root-map-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <header class="section-head section-head--split">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">ACC. ROOT-MAP-01</p>
          <h2>Living Infrastructure Index</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="section-copy">
          The visible attraction is not the whole structure. Beneath it runs a quieter network:
          roots, memory, patience, and living continuity.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="root-map" role="img" aria-label="Root network connecting Deep Garden to all attraction locations">
        <svg class="root-svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M50 50 C35 20 22 17 12 22" />
          <path d="M50 50 C70 22 80 18 91 24" />
          <path d="M50 50 C25 55 14 55 8 60" />
          <path d="M50 50 C75 55 85 55 93 60" />
          <path d="M50 50 C35 80 24 82 15 84" />
          <path d="M50 50 C67 78 78 82 89 84" />
          <path d="M50 50 C50 20 50 12 50 5" />
          <path d="M50 50 C50 80 50 88 50 95" />
        </svg>
        <div class="root-node root-node--center">Deep Garden</div>
        <div class="root-node root-node--n1">Midway</div>
        <div class="root-node root-node--n2">Museum</div>
        <div class="root-node root-node--n3">Bob's Fortune</div>
        <div class="root-node root-node--n4">Ghost's Workshop</div>
        <div class="root-node root-node--n5">Wedding Chapel</div>
        <div class="root-node root-node--n6 root-node--warning">Cathedral</div>
        <div class="root-node root-node--n7">Crossroads</div>
        <div class="root-node root-node--n8">Corporate Glasshouse</div>
      </div>

      <p class="map-caption">Wiring carries signals. Roots carry memory.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 04. Deep Garden Artifacts ── -->
  <section id="deep-garden" class="garden-section deep-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="artifact-grid artifact-grid--deep">
        <article class="artifact-card artifact-card--deep">
          <span class="artifact-idx">A</span>
          <h3>Seed Archive</h3>
          <p>Dream Crown, Archive Courtyard, Crossroads Atlas, Signal Herbarium, and Dormant Cabinet 7.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="artifact-card artifact-card--deep">
          <span class="artifact-idx">B</span>
          <h3>Compost Notes</h3>
          <p>Some ideas do not fail. They become soil.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="artifact-card artifact-card--deep">
          <span class="artifact-idx">C</span>
          <h3>Dormant Ideas</h3>
          <p>Not ready yet does not mean abandoned. Some roots grow in silence for years before finding light.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="artifact-card artifact-card--deep artifact-card--warning">
          <span class="artifact-idx artifact-idx--warn">!</span>
          <h3>Root Warnings</h3>
          <p>Do not pull at active roots. Do not follow roots toward the Cathedral without escort. Do not confuse dormancy with abandonment.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="artifact-card artifact-card--deep">
          <span class="artifact-idx">W</span>
          <h3>Warden's Field Notes</h3>
          <p>The difference between delay and incubation is care.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="artifact-card artifact-card--deep">
          <span class="artifact-idx">?</span>
          <h3>Things Not Ready Yet</h3>
          <p>A holding shelf for ideas that still have heat but no shape. Come back when the season changes.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 08. Plant an Idea ── -->
  <section id="plant-idea" class="garden-section plant-section">
    <div class="section-inner plant-inner">
      <header class="section-head section-head--split">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Planting Station</p>
          <h2>Plant an Idea</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="section-copy">Every idea is a seed. Not every seed should become a project immediately. Give it the right conditions and check back.</p>
      </header>

      <div class="planting-station">
        <form id="seedForm" class="seed-form" autocomplete="off">
          <label>
            Idea Name
            <input id="ideaName" name="ideaName" maxlength="80" placeholder="Give your idea a name..." />
          </label>
          <label>
            What sparked it?
            <textarea id="ideaSpark" name="ideaSpark" maxlength="300" placeholder="What moment, observation, or question lit this idea?"></textarea>
          </label>
          <label>
            Why isn't it ready?
            <textarea id="ideaBlock" name="ideaBlock" maxlength="300" placeholder="What's missing, unclear, or unresolved right now?"></textarea>
          </label>
          <label>
            What might help it grow?
            <textarea id="ideaNeed" name="ideaNeed" maxlength="300" placeholder="What resources, connections, or conditions would support it?"></textarea>
          </label>
          <label>
            When should it be checked again?
            <select id="reviewTime" name="reviewTime">
              <option>Later</option>
              <option>7 days</option>
              <option>30 days</option>
              <option>Next season</option>
              <option>When Bob stops laughing</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <div class="form-actions">
            <button type="button" id="clearSeed" class="garden-btn garden-btn--ghost">Clear</button>
            <button type="button" id="downloadSeed" class="garden-btn garden-btn--primary">Download Packet</button>
          </div>
        </form>

        <div id="plantingConfirmed" class="planting-confirmed" aria-live="polite" hidden>
          <p class="confirm-eyebrow mono">PLANTING CONFIRMED</p>
          <div class="confirm-divider"></div>
          <p class="confirm-line">Your specimen has been logged.</p>
          <p class="confirm-line confirm-line--dim">The Garden keeps its own records.<br/>We do not guarantee what grows.<br/>We do not guarantee it stays where you plant it.</p>
          <p class="confirm-accession mono" id="confirmAccession">ACC. GARDEN-——</p>
          <div class="confirm-divider"></div>
          <div class="confirm-actions">
            <a href="/deep-garden" class="confirm-btn mono">RETURN TO THE GARDEN</a>
            <button type="button" id="plantAnother" class="confirm-btn confirm-btn--ghost mono">PLANT ANOTHER</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="seed-preview-panel">
          <div class="seed-packet">
            <p class="packet-kicker">Deep Garden Archive</p>
            <h3 id="packetTitle">Seed of Potential</h3>
            <div class="packet-illustration" aria-hidden="true">✦</div>
            <dl class="packet-data">
              <div class="packet-row">
                <dt>Idea</dt>
                <dd id="packetIdea">Your idea's name will appear here</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="packet-row">
                <dt>Status</dt>
                <dd>Dormant</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="packet-row">
                <dt>Planted</dt>
                <dd id="packetDate"></dd>
              </div>
              <div class="packet-row">
                <dt>Review</dt>
                <dd id="packetReview">Later</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
            <p class="warden-stamp">Warden Note: Let it rest.</p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 09. Warden's Notes ── -->
  <section class="garden-section warden-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Filed Under: Long-Term Care</p>
      <div class="note-grid">
        <blockquote>Not every idea should become a task immediately.</blockquote>
        <blockquote>Patience is structure in biological form.</blockquote>
        <blockquote>A living system knows when not to act.</blockquote>
        <blockquote>Clarity is often what remains after urgency leaves.</blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 10. Next Doorways ── -->
  <section class="garden-section doorway-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Next Doorways</p>
      <div class="doorway-grid">
        <a href="/attraction" class="doorway-card">Return to the Attraction</a>
        <a href="/museum" class="doorway-card">Visit the Museum File</a>
        <a href="/workshop" class="doorway-card">Access Ghost's Workshop</a>
        <a href="/" class="doorway-card">Return to the Crossroads</a>
        <a href="/cathedral" class="doorway-card doorway-card--danger">Do Not Follow Roots Toward the Cathedral</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 11. Garden Footer ── -->
  <footer class="garden-footer">
    <strong>Yasuragi / Deep Garden</strong>
    <span>Root Systems Stable</span>
    <em>Somewhere above, the Midway is still making noise.</em>
  </footer>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ── Garden palette (local overrides) ── */
  :root {
    --g-teal: #36d5cd;
    --g-teal-dim: rgba(54, 213, 205, 0.28);
    --g-amber: #d3a85b;
    --g-paper: #e7dbc0;
    --g-paper-ink: #2d2418;
    --g-ink: #f1ead8;
    --g-muted: #a99f8e;
    --g-moss: #547249;
    --g-green: #85a96d;
    --g-line: rgba(184, 145, 78, 0.28);
    --g-soil: #0a0f0c;
    --g-stone: #18201b;
    --g-display: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    --g-max: 1180px;
    /* scroll descent motion vars — updated by JS */
    --p: 0;
    --surfaceOpacity: 1;
    --cutawayOpacity: 0;
    --deepOpacity: 0;
    --rootOpacity: 0;
    --signalOpacity: 0;
    --mistOpacity: 0.25;
    --surfaceY: 0px;
    --cutawayY: 40px;
    --deepY: 80px;
    --leafY: 0px;
    --rootY: 80px;
    --surfaceScale: 1;
    --cutawayScale: 1.04;
    --deepScale: 1.08;
  }

  /* ── Depth marker ── */
  .depth-marker {
    position: fixed;
    left: 1.25rem;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    z-index: 80;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .depth-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--g-muted);
    opacity: 0.48;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .depth-dot {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 9px;
    height: 9px;
    border: 1px solid var(--g-teal);
    border-radius: 50%;
    transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .depth-link.active {
    color: var(--g-teal);
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .depth-link.active .depth-dot {
    background: var(--g-teal);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(54, 213, 205, 0.8);
  }

  /* ── Shared typography ── */
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    color: var(--g-amber);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .hero-flavor,
  .section-note {
    font-family: var(--g-display);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--g-muted);
  }

  /* ── Buttons ── */
  .garden-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 44px;
    padding: 0.7rem 1.1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--g-line);
    transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }
  .garden-btn--primary {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #d9b66f, #a77b34);
    color: #07100d;
    border-color: transparent;
  }
  .garden-btn--primary:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #e5c47c, #b88840);
    color: #07100d;
  }
  .garden-btn--ghost {
    background: rgba(8, 13, 11, 0.68);
    color: var(--g-teal);
    border-color: var(--g-teal-dim);
  }
  .garden-btn--ghost:hover {
    background: rgba(54, 213, 205, 0.08);
    color: var(--g-teal);
    border-color: rgba(54, 213, 205, 0.5);
  }

  /* ── Status card ── */
  .status-card {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: min(300px, 100%);
    padding: 1.1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--g-teal-dim);
    background: rgba(8, 19, 17, 0.78);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }
  .status-card--deep {
    border-color: rgba(54, 213, 205, 0.35);
    background: rgba(4, 10, 8, 0.85);
  }
  .status-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--g-teal);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .status-card strong {
    font-family: var(--g-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #e8dec7;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .status-card span {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: #9fb8ac;
  }

  /* ── Sections ── */
  .garden-section {
    padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem) 0;
  }
  .surface-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a110d 0%, #080e0b 100%);
  }
  .root-map-section {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(54, 213, 205, 0.06), transparent 32rem),
      #070d09;
  }
  .deep-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #060c09 0%, #040806 100%);
  }
  .plant-section {
    background: #060b08;
  }
  .warden-section {
    background: #050808;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }
  .doorway-section {
    background: #040706;
  }
  .section-inner {
    width: min(var(--g-max), calc(100vw - 2rem));
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .plant-inner {
    width: min(1280px, calc(100vw - 2rem));
  }
  .section-head {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .section-head--split {
    max-width: none;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr minmax(260px, 420px);
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: end;
  }
  .section-head h2 {
    font-family: var(--g-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1.0;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--g-ink);
    margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
  }
  .section-copy {
    color: var(--g-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .section-note {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  /* ── Artifact grid ── */
  .artifact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .artifact-card {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 240px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(22, 36, 30, 0.94), rgba(8, 14, 12, 0.94)),
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 10%, rgba(54, 213, 205, 0.10), transparent 16rem);
    border: 1px solid var(--g-line);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .artifact-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 1rem;
    right: 1rem;
    width: 54px;
    height: 54px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(184,145,78,0.15);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .artifact-card--deep {
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(12, 19, 16, 0.96), rgba(5, 8, 6, 0.96)),
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 10%, rgba(133,169,109,0.07), transparent 14rem);
    border-color: rgba(54, 213, 205, 0.18);
  }
  .artifact-card--warning {
    border-color: rgba(182, 83, 70, 0.45);
  }
  .artifact-idx {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border: 1px solid var(--g-teal-dim);
    color: var(--g-teal);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .artifact-idx--warn {
    border-color: rgba(182,83,70,0.55);
    color: #ff8c82;
  }
  .artifact-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--g-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--g-ink);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .artifact-card p {
    color: #b7ae9d;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    margin: 0;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .artifact-card small {
    display: block;
    color: var(--g-muted);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: auto;
  }
  .quote-card blockquote {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
    font-family: var(--g-display);
    font-size: 1.45rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #e5d6b8;
    flex: 1;
  }

  /* ── Scroll descent ── */
  .descent-stage {
    position: relative;
    height: 460vh;
  }
  .descent-viewport {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #020403;
  }
  .descent-viewport::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(5,8,7,0.08), rgba(5,8,7,0.4) 48%, rgba(5,8,7,0.92));
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 3;
  }
  .motion-layer {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    will-change: opacity, transform;
  }
  .surface-image {
    background-image: url('/yasuragi-garden-hero.png');
    opacity: var(--surfaceOpacity);
    transform: translate3d(0, var(--surfaceY), 0) scale(var(--surfaceScale));
  }
  .cutaway-image {
    background-image: url('/root-transition-cutaway.png');
    opacity: var(--cutawayOpacity);
    transform: translate3d(0, var(--cutawayY), 0) scale(var(--cutawayScale));
  }
  .deep-image {
    background-image: url('/deep-garden-hero.png');
    opacity: var(--deepOpacity);
    transform: translate3d(0, var(--deepY), 0) scale(var(--deepScale));
  }
  .leaves-layer {
    background-image: url('/foreground-leaves-lanterns.png');
    opacity: calc(var(--surfaceOpacity) * 0.9);
    transform: translate3d(0, var(--leafY), 0) scale(1.03);
  }
  .roots-layer {
    background-image: url('/foreground-roots-cables.png');
    opacity: var(--rootOpacity);
    transform: translate3d(0, var(--rootY), 0) scale(1.06);
  }
  .signal-layer {
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 130px 90px at 22% 66%, rgba(54,213,205,0.6) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 95px 65px at 48% 72%, rgba(54,213,205,0.5) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 110px 75px at 72% 64%, rgba(54,213,205,0.55) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 75px 52px at 36% 80%, rgba(54,213,205,0.38) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 85px 58px at 83% 74%, rgba(54,213,205,0.42) 0%, transparent 100%);
    background-size: 100% 100%;
    opacity: var(--signalOpacity);
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
  }
  .mist-layer {
    background-image: url('/mist-noise-overlay.png');
    opacity: var(--mistOpacity);
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
    animation: mistDrift 18s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  .shaft-vignette-layer {
    background-image: url('/shaft-vignette.png');
    opacity: calc(0.35 + var(--p) * 0.6);
  }
  @keyframes mistDrift {
    from { transform: translate3d(-2%, 0, 0) scale(1.04); }
    to   { transform: translate3d(2%, -1%, 0) scale(1.07); }
  }
  .descent-copy {
    position: absolute;
    right: clamp(1rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    bottom: clamp(2rem, 10vw, 7rem);
    z-index: 5;
    width: min(520px, calc(100vw - 6rem));
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(5, 8, 7, 0.58);
    border: 1px solid rgba(54, 213, 205, 0.2);
